name: luhn
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "luhn" %}
{% set version = "0.2.0" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: 917174cecce8bcbbe56ac0d904dbedd06594b21b6f31d5a3ec161d455b0e59f7

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 1
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - luhn
    
about:
  home: "https://github.com/mmcloughlin/luhn"
  license: "MIT"
  license_family: "MIT"
  license_file: "LICENSE"
  summary: "Generate and verify Luhn check digits"
  doc_url: "https://pypi.org/project/luhn/"
  dev_url: "https://github.com/mmcloughlin/luhn"

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - mxr-conda
    - mwilson8
    - rluria14
    - benhuff
